text: The List of JEF United Ichihara Chiba players is evolving. The history of the team is created by its players. JEF United Ichihara ChibaIn 2005, the club changed its name from "JEF United Ichihara". In the current name, JEF is a complex acronym. JEF stands for East Japan Railway Company=_JE_ and Furukawa Electric=_F_.
